{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1734786703.806132", "card_id": "Q_7298082565", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 年 11 月，人民币重回全球第四大最活跃货币，占比升至 3.89%，这反映了哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "环球银行金融电信协会（Swift）当地时间 12 月 18 日发布的人民币月度报告和数据统计显示，今年 11 月，人民币在全球支付货币中的占比升至 3.89%，全球支付占比排名向前一位，升至第四大最活跃货币。具体而言，与 10 月相比，人民币支付金额总体增加了 22.12%，同时所有货币支付金额总体减少了 8.09%。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7267db43b1534358309fe43548edfd4a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "236 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7298082565"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI8fmNm7u69PZCEAMaCTExMjQzNjMxOCC+3I+7BjAAOLsBQAByCjcyOTgwODI1NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1734786703.807025", "card_id": "Q_7292229806", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 25 考研政治肖四「翻车」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近十年最难的一次政治考试，考研过来人们如何看待这次的题目"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-19cf830c534431fc9194d40d87988b58_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "184 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7292229806"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8fmNm7u69PZCEAMaCTExMjQzNTE1NCCgvI+7BjAAODpAAXIKNzI5MjIyOTgwNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1734786703.807396", "card_id": "Q_7292205563", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 25 考研英语的难度，哪个模块最难？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "考生评价英语一出了图表作文，阅读时长半小时一篇，政治和英语今年双双开大嘛"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7751bf1d720debf98b92f37a1ffccf0f_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "150 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7292205563"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI8fmNm7u69PZCEAMaCTExMjQzNTE0OCCgvI+7BjAAOJECQAJyCjcyOTIyMDU1NjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1734786703.807784", "card_id": "Q_7350148106", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "10 月美债前三大海外债主日本、中国、英国均减持美债，中国连续第四个月减持，基于哪些经济因素的考量？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 12 月 20 日，美国财政部公布的数据显示，2024 年 10 月，美债前三大海外债主日本、中国、英国均减持美国国债。 美国财政部 2024 年 10 月国际资本流动报告（TIC）显示，日本 10 月减持 206 亿美元美国国债，持仓规模为 11027 亿美元，依然是美国第一大债主。 中国 10 月减持 119 亿美元美国国债至 7601 亿美元，是今年 6 月二次加仓后连续第四个月减持。10 月中国减持 119 亿美元美国国债，连续第四个月减持 _ 金改实验室 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f6e6e7d874d1fb294f1987a0c10ecca_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7350148106"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8fmNm7u69PZCEAMaCTExMjQ0NjcxNiC4k5O7BjAAOC5AA3IKNzM1MDE0ODEwNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1734786703.808298", "card_id": "Q_7389495682", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e